des: Rock, Boogie, and Blues—that’s radiodaddio! Enjoy iconic classic rock hits from the '60s, '70s, and 80s, along with underrated gems, good-time boogie, and soulful blues, all curated by Michael J, a seasoned Classic Rock programmer with nearly 50 years of experience. Radiodaddio is a vibrant community for rock lovers to rediscover the soundtrack of their lives and uncover hidden musical treasures.
